OL,3,CFour men arrested over hedgehog spray
OL,4,Cpainted blue
OL,6,FFour men have been arrested after a
OL,7,Fhedgehog was found spray painted blue
OL,8,Fand yellow in Leeds.
OL,10,FThe hedgehog, which has been named
OL,11,FHoney, was found covered in paint in a
OL,12,Fgarden in Yeadon.
OL,14,FWest Yorkshire Police say four men
OL,15,Faged 44, 21, 17 and 15 were arrested
OL,16,Fon suspicion of causing unnecessary
OL,17,Fsuffering to a protected animal.
OL,19,FAll four have been bailed while
OL,20,Ffurther enquiries take place.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
