SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784900897
OL,3,CFour men arrested over hedgehog spray
OL,4,Cpainted blue
OL,6,FThe hedgehog was taken to Prickly Pigs
OL,7,FHedgehog Charity in Otley to be
OL,8,Ftreated and they are still working to
OL,9,Fremove the paint a week on.
OL,11,FDiane Cook, from Prickly Pigs Hedgehog
OL,12,FCharity, says: "We are having to use a
OL,13,Fbrush and scrape off the paint that's
OL,14,Fon there. Because it was so thick, her
OL,15,Fspines were actually clumped together.
OL,17,F"Obviously, for a hedgehog their
OL,18,Fspines are their only natural form of
OL,19,Fprotecting themselves.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
