FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784900897
OL,3,CFour men arrested over hedgehog spray
OL,4,Cpainted blue
OL,6,F"Although her breathing is much better
OL,7,Fnow, she came in with a terrible type
OL,8,Fof breathing problems. She was
OL,9,Fwheezing which we suspect was a result
OL,10,Fof potentially breathing in the fumes
OL,11,Fof the paint she's been covered in.
OL,13,F"People just unfortunately don't think
OL,14,Fwhen it comes to wildlife, they don't.
OL,15,FCertainly poor Honey here, this wasn't
OL,16,Fan accidental incident."
OL,18,FThe charity say Honey has a long way
OL,19,Fto go but with medication they are
OL,20,Fhopeful that she will make a full
OL,21,Frecovery.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/3
